Package: stansurv
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Survival Analysis using 'Stan'
Version: 0.0.0-9000
Author@R: c(person("Sam", "Brilleman", 
                   email = "sam.brilleman@monash.edu" 
						    	 role = c("cre", "aut")))
Description: Fit Bayesian survival (i.e. time-to-event ) models 
    with the back-end estimation carried out using 'Stan'. The 
		models are pre-compiled. Users specify the model using customary
    R formula syntax and data frames.		
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.4.0),
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.0),
    methods
Imports:
    rstan (>= 2.17.2),
    rstantools (>= 1.4.0),
    stats,
    survival (>= 2.40.1),
    utils
NeedsCompilation: yes
VignetteBuilder: knitr
BugReports: https://github.com/sambrilleman/stansurv/issues
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
